  "text": "The LSS was a multicenter feasibility trial that randomized 1,660 participants to low-dose CT screening and 1,558 participants to chest x-ray [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Of the 522 participants with a positive baseline CT screen, 12% (n ϭ 63) underwent biopsies, of which 33 were resection or open surgical biopsies. In total, 89 biopsies were performed on 62 participants, of which 36 were diagnosed with lung cancer. Twenty-six of the participants undergoing biopsies did not have lung cancer.",
